longBusinessSummary: Aquarius AI Inc., a programmatic advertising technology company, provides digital branding and advertising services in the United States. It builds a technology platform for video that allows advertisers to carefully select where their ads are placed safeguarding a brand's reputation by ensuring their advertising is only associated with brand safe inventory. The company is based in Vancouver, Canada.
